# incus-spawn appliance — BusyBox init configuration
#
# Gettys are started by rcS (not here) to avoid errors on non-existent devices.
# BusyBox init opens the device in the id field before executing the command,
# which produces "can't open" errors for devices that don't exist on this backend.

::sysinit:/etc/init.d/rcS
::shutdown:/etc/init.d/rcK
